10,000 km is a spanish romantic drama film directed by carlos &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; . it film stars natalia tena and david &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; as a couple trying to make their relationship work , while one lives in barcelona and the other in los angeles . the film had its world premiere on march 10 , 2014 at the sxsw film festival and received the special jury recognition for best acting duo . the film was released on may 16 , 2014 in spain and on july 10 , 2015 , in a limited release and through video on demand by broad green pictures in the united states .